# Production redirect placeholders.
# Replace example.com with the real canonical domain before deploying.
#
# Netlify-style examples:
# http://example.com/*  https://example.com/:splat  301!
# http://www.example.com/*  https://example.com/:splat  301!
# https://www.example.com/*  https://example.com/:splat  301!
#
# Cloudflare equivalent:
# 1. Always Use HTTPS: enabled
# 2. Redirect www.example.com/* to https://example.com/$1
# 3. Set VITE_CANONICAL_URL=https://example.com
